# Ctrl+6 switches to Source tab (Auth was inserted as slot 4 → Source is now
# slot 6 in the Body/Headers/Params/Auth/Vars/Source tab strip); typing fills
# source_buffer; http.paste_source parses + auto-switches to Body tab.

write anchor.txt anchor
open anchor.txt

command http.new

key ctrl+6

expect screen contains "Script"

type "curl 'https://api.example.com/users'"

command http.paste_source

expect screen contains "api.example.com"
expect screen contains "GET"
expect screen contains "Body"
